Class DeliverySelectionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • javafx.event.Event
        • components.mapcanvas.DeliverySelectionEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class DeliverySelectionEvent
extends javafx.event.Event
    This class corresponds to the selection of a delivery address in the mapCanvas, it is usually send to the MapScreen which will update the corresponding tooltip.
